items.question: How about PhotoMaker V2?
items.answer: PhotoMaker V2 Improved ID Fidelity and Better Controllability than PhotoMaker V1

items.question: How to use PhotoMaker V2?
items.answer: How to use PhotoMaker V2 can be found in https://github.com/TencentARC/PhotoMaker

items.question: How many photos can I customize at once?
items.answer: You can upload and customize up to 4 photos simultaneously in a single batch.

items.question: What file formats are supported?
items.answer: We support common image formats including JPG, PNG, and WebP.

items.question: How long does the generation process take?
items.answer: Most customize complete within 10-30 seconds, depending on the complexity.

items.question: Can I use custom prompts?
items.answer: Yes, you can provide custom text prompts to guide PhotoMaker customize process.

items.question: The Technology Behind PhotoMaker?
items.answer: PhotoMaker utilizes advanced transformer-based models and the latest AI research of PhotoMaker V2
